CreateDomain is the only work-request-backed
mutation in the visible SDK contract. The
runtime stores the create work request, waits
through GetWorkRequest, and rereads GetDomain
once that work request succeeds.
UpdateDomain returns the concrete Domain body
directly, so update projects status from the
response body without a separate follow-up read.
DeleteDomain returns no work-request identifier.
The runtime issues delete once, then confirms
DELETED or NOT_FOUND through GetDomain or
ListDomains rereads before releasing the
finalizer.
Pre-create reuse and delete-time list fallback
both key off exact compartmentId plus domainName
and optionally reuse lifecycleState and status
as narrowing filters when the CR sets them.
end note
